---
import MiniTerminal from './MiniTerminal.astro';
---

<section class="about" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-h">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div class="about-copy">
      <span class="tape">the bill of goods</span>
      <h2 id="about-h">Why “trash”?</h2>

      <p>
        I call these <strong>Trash Tools</strong> on purpose. Most of the code was written with
        an LLM riding shotgun, so by some measures, it becomes “less valuable” as it wasn't
        hand-made entirely by a human. I get it.
      </p>
      <p>
        Each tool here fills some need I had — translating documents without paying a fortune,
        wrangling my retro game collection, impositioning books for printing and binding,
        navigating an old Japanese MMORPG withough losing my mind. Nearly always, alternatives
        were expensive, tedious, or just didn’t exist, so I made these instead. AI let me do it
        in my spare time. The alternative was "no tool gets made." So that was my choice.
      </p>
      <p>
        The code’s all right there in the repos, robot fingerprints and all. This site is one of
        them too — same robot, same rules. It's probably not as good or clean as if I'd
        architected and written them all by hand. But they DO exist, flawed as they are, and
        for me that means I can get other things done.
      </p>
      <p>
        So welcome to my trash heap.
      </p>

      <div class="signoff">
        <p class="who">— Scott Harper</p>
        <p class="role">piler of trash</p>
        <div class="contact">
          <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:scott@trashtools.net">scott@trashtools.net</a>
          <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <a class="contact-link" href="https://github.com/AberrantWolf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
            >github.com/AberrantWolf</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-aside" aria-label="A small terminal to poke at">
      <MiniTerminal />
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    background:
      linear-gradient(var(--paper-2), var(--paper-2)) padding-box,
      radial-gradient(80% 60% at 100% 0%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--teal) 8%, transparent), transparent 60%);
    border-block: 1px dashed var(--line-strong);
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  .about-copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 1.3rem + 2.4vw, 3rem);
    margin: 0.7rem 0 1.1rem;
  }
  .about-copy p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 38rem;
  }
  .about-copy strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .signoff {
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
  }
  .who {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.1rem !important;
  }
  .role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem !important;
  }
  .contact {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .contact .dot {
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .about-aside {
    position: sticky;
    top: 1.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-aside {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
